sentence: What is the highest place of the Urals?
What is the second highest mountain on Earth?
sparqlQald: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Mountain> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/elevation> ?elevation } ORDER BY DESC(?elevation) OFFSET 1 LIMIT 1

sentence: Which mountains are higher than the Nanga Parbat?
sparqlQald: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nanga_Parbat> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/elevation> ?elevation . ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Mountain> { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/elevation> ?otherelevation } UNION { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/property/elevationM> ?otherelevation } FILTER ( ?otherelevation > ?elevation ) }

sentence: What is the highest mountain in Saxony Germany?
sparqlQald: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT ?m WHERE { ?m dbo:mountainRange dbr:Ore_Mountains ; dbo:elevation ?height } ORDER BY DESC(?height) LIMIT 1

sentence: How many people live in the capital of Australia?
sparqlQald: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?num WHERE { res:Australia dbo:capital ?x . ?x dbo:populationTotal ?num }

sentence: Is Michelle Obama the wife of Barack Obama?
sparqlQald: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> ASK WHERE { res:Barack_Obama dbo:spouse res:Michelle_Obama }
